WEBVTT

00:03:59.295 --> 00:04:00.487
(Vicheko)

00:04:00.511 --> 00:04:03.254
Msaada wetu mara nyingi hausaidii.

00:04:03.748 --> 00:04:06.173
Msaada wetu mara nyingi ni sumu.

00:04:06.824 --> 00:04:09.620
Na msaada ni upande chanya wa udhibiti.

00:04:10.836 --> 00:04:13.310
Acha kusaidia sana.

00:04:13.334 --> 00:04:16.791
Usisambaze msaada wako na wema kwa kila mtu.

00:04:16.815 --> 00:04:19.327
(Vicheko)

00:04:19.351 --> 00:04:21.012
(Makofi)

00:04:21.036 --> 00:04:23.009
Hii inatuleta kwa namba nne:

00:04:23.033 --> 00:04:26.917
kila mtu amevunjika,
amevunjwa, ana wivu na hofu zake,

00:04:26.941 --> 00:04:29.916
hata wanaoonekana kuwa pamoja zaidi.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:32.379
Wako kama wewe kuliko unavzoweza kuamini,